<p>BYU-Idaho accepts many AP and IB exams for credit consideration. Students who complete an AP exam with a score of 3 or above may receive University credit in that subject area according to the approved University list. Students who complete an IB course with a grade of 5 or above may receive University credit in that subject area according to the approved University list.</p>
